<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFRosenbusch_B2006">Rosenbusch B (November 2006). "The contradictory information on the distribution of non-disjunction and pre-division in female gametes". <i>Hum. Reprod.</i> <b>21</b> (11): 2739–42. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<span class="neverexpand"><a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1093%2Fhumrep%2Fdel122" class="external text" title="http://dx.doi.org/10.1093%2Fhumrep%2Fdel122" rel="nofollow">10.1093/humrep/del122</a></span>. <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16982661" class="external" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/16982661">PMID 16982661</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=The+contradictory+information+on+the+distribution+of+non-disjunction+and+pre-division+in+female+gametes&amp;rft.jtitle=Hum.+Reprod.&amp;rft.aulast=Rosenbusch+B&amp;rft.au=Rosenbusch+B&amp;rft.date=November+2006&amp;rft.volume=21&amp;rft.issue=11&amp;rft.pages=2739%E2%80%9342&amp;rft_id=info:doi/10.1093%2Fhumrep%2Fdel122&amp;rft_id=info:pmid/16982661&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Meiosis"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ol>
